import React from "react";
import { Link, NavLink } from "react-router-dom"

export default function Navbar() {
    return ( <
        >
        <
        nav id = "navbar" >

        <
        Link to = "/"
        className = "routelinks"
        id = "homelink" > #VANLIFE < /Link>

        <
        div id = "link-right" >
        <
        NavLink to = "/host"
        className = {
            ({ isActive }) => isActive ? "routelink-active" : "routelinks" } > Host < /NavLink> <
        NavLink to = "/about"
        className = {
            ({ isActive }) => isActive ? "routelink-active" : "routelinks" } > About < /NavLink> <
        NavLink to = "/vans"
        className = {
            ({ isActive }) => isActive ? "routelink-active" : "routelinks" } > Vans < /NavLink> <
        /div>

        <
        /nav>

        <
        />
    )
}
